  lines:
  - "Faction Member: \u2026\u2026."
  - "Faction Member: I heard from the other guy earlier that you\u2019re in"
  - "Faction Member: Just so you know, I can\u2019t stand people like you, obsessed
    with family, having it be the only damn thing you care about. "
  - "Faction Member: Everyone in this fucking town is obsessed with it, you wanna
    go out or do anything it\u2019s always meeting people, seeing friends."
  - 'Faction Member:  Government would never dare to think of giving anything nice
    to someone like me.'
  - "Faction Member:  But whatever, to get you up to speed, I imagine you\u2019ve
    heard those rumours going around, about the hiding of symptoms? "
  - "Faction Member:  That\u2019s all, expect to be contacted later, we\u2019ll have
    more for you to do."
